{"tid":798683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人越大越怕係whatsapp group留言？","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:53.000Z","uid":57036,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06cb22f8e041d87a82e21da1d27cd88a7d5599df","tid":798683,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"小學/中學/大學/同事whatsapp group都有<br />\n出黎做野之後<br />\n同好多朋友都見少左疏落左<br />\n都係靠whatsapp聯繫<br />\n但越黎越多group死左<br />\n<br />\n有時share下d新聞yo下個group<br />\n&quot;喂搶唔搶到子華門票呀？&quot;<br />\n&quot;今年港姐選左隻身長頸鹿喎&quot;<br />\n不過收到d藍剔真係好沮喪<br />\n又成為話題終結者<br />\n個group假假地都有7,8個人<br />\n究竟佢地係對篇新聞冇性趣定對我冇性趣<br />\n反而d新識既同事/朋友都會比下面9 up幾句吹下水<br />\n<br />\n有個老死呻: 而家d老細真係好惡頂<br />\n我回佢: 搞咩呀<br />\n咁都可以藍剔收皮<br />\n但其他人問佢又會秒回<br />\n自此我就冇再comment過佢所有野<br />\n<br />\n打開你個whatsapp<br />\n望下有幾多個朋友group仲有活躍<br />\n而你又唔怕dead air暢所欲言既，陪你9up既<br />\n恭喜你<br />\n請好好珍惜個group<br />\n因為呢份情唔係必然唔係永恆既<br />\n<br />\n利申: 岩岩又mute多左一個group，唔再comment，越黎越怕係group出聲<br />\n叫春完畢，我番番出去做野先"},{"pid":"8bcc9998f19b9bd1173323c040879907b68e0a3d","tid":798683,"uid":50779,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a20f383a97f7758be693d3336b19a778168f7b67","tid":798683,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fcdbdf1f79cf979817345a34faa98d41702b813","tid":798683,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"人越<del>大</del>毒"},{"pid":"ad0c535f769a0cbdbc477c9adecc2db3220d4cfe","tid":798683,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"越大越唔夠膽鳩up<br />\n變左透明人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567b303c3e5e9918201c0b0f9c8aef64a5859500","tid":798683,"uid":77730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bcc9998f19b9bd1173323c040879907b68e0a3d","tid":798683,"uid":50779,"li